            "heading": "Our Arccos Gen 4 Starter Bundle game tracking system includes:",
            "content": "<ul><li>15 Smart Sensors & 1 Putter Sensor. Smart Sensors are weather-resistant, ultra-light, and feature a long lasting battery.</li><li>1 Air Wearable - Automatically track shots right from your front pocket, without a phone. Lightweight shot tracking device syncs with the Arccos app. Includes a wireless charging case that provides safe storage and powers up to 12 rounds.</li><li>1st year's membership to the award winning Arccos app* (New Members only).</li><li>Annual Free Sensor Renewal Program: Get 5 new smart sensors every year to use on additional clubs or as replacements. <a href=\"https://arccos-dev.myshopify.com/blogs/community/arccos-member-free-sensors-program\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Arccos Member Free Sensors Program\">Learn More.</a></li><li>The latest shot tracking software on both iOS and Android platforms.</li></ul>",
