            "content": "<ul><li>A.I. Powered GPS Rangefinder: Get precise yardages adjusted in real time for wind, elevation/slope, temperature, humidity & altitude.</li><li>Smart Club Distances: Know how far you really hit all your clubs in every situation.</li><li>Strokes Gained Insights: Pinpoint your strengths and weaknesses based on your target handicap, so you know exactly which part of your game to work on.</li><li>AI Strategy: Tour-proven, real-time strategy including club recommendations and precise targets for every shot.</li><li>Green Maps: Advanced slope visualization helps you see the break, understand green contours, and plan smarter approaches and putts.</li></ul>",
