    "testimonials_F7gWYb": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_RkbdTU": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>I've been playing golf for 20 years now, been an Arccos user for 5 months, over that 5 month span I've gone from a 15 handicap to a 10.</p>",
            "author": "Zach K",
            "author_info": "Arccos Member",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_video": false,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_7zEB4B": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Arccos tells you what kind of golfer you are. It tells you your entire golf game. For me it's more about helping me to improve my game. Telling me where I'm at, and where I want to be.</p>",
            "author": "Luiza A",
            "author_info": "Arccos Member",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_video": false,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Kmtmt8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>I’ve been using Arccos for over a year now. The most beneficial thing for me is preparation for tournaments. It allows me to track my stats and Strokes Gained metrics and that’s huge for validating my practice to make sure I am improving.</p>",
            "author": "Zach P",
            "author_info": "Arccos Member",
